{"tid":1055512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【埃國空難】中國大使館證1港人罹難　疑為中大畢業生遺妻兒","createTime":"2019-03-10T15:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T15:05:04.000Z","uid":20933,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"1c488a906093e41ce0cc2b8d2dc7c76ec876e245","tid":1055512,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190310/large/1552220589_6437.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190310%2Flarge%2F1552220589_6437.jpg&h=5cc3ace7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n埃塞俄比亞航空一架737-800MAX客機，今日在從首都亞的斯亞貝巴（Addis Ababa），飛往肯雅首都內羅比（Nairobi）途中墜毁，機上149名乘客、8名機組人員，無人生還。中國駐埃塞俄比亞大使館向《蘋果》證實，8名中國乘客全部罹難，當中包括一名在聯合國工作的香港人。<br />\n<br />\n央視在微博指，從中國駐肯雅大使館確認其中3名中國乘客的資料，其顯示的名單包括中國電子科技集團貿易公司職員周圓（37歲）、中國國航的金也淘（32歲）及曾成毅3人，其中，曾成毅為「聯合國環境署職員」的「籍貫」一欄中標註了「香港」二字，但備註顯示「待確認」，周、金二人則籍貫不詳。不過，央視隨即撤走了該則微博。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐埃塞俄比亞大使館媒體發言人向《蘋果》記者證實有一名香港人罹難，而該港人為聯合國工作，但該發言人基於私隱理由，拒絕透露該港人姓名及年齡等資料，因而本報未能確認是否為央視公佈死者名單中提及的「曾成毅」。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，於2018年12月的中大校友期刊中，曾介紹2004年工商管理學系畢業生曾成毅，指他在非洲肯雅聯合國辦事處工作，早前回港擔任中大全球研究課程其中一節課的客席講師，分享對可持續發展的看法。<br />\n<br />\n據曾成毅的妻子親屬在網絡上分享生活點滴，指曾在教堂認識了妻子張思明，二人一直在聯合國教科文組織任職，2016年被派往肯雅工作，在異鄉育有一名兒子「林林」。該親屬形容：「聯合國組織福利甚佳，一幢房子4房2廳，於是婆婆（曾的外母）便火速飛往陌生的國度，途經迪拜（杜拜）轉機，十來個小時旅程，忘卻疲憊，馬上投入家庭樂之氛圍中。」空難發生時，曾成毅的妻兒未有隨行。<br />\n<br />\n至於機上是否有香港旅客，香港旅遊業議會總幹事陳張樂怡向《蘋果》表示，暫時沒有收到相關報告，也沒有收到旅行團受影響的報告。本港入境處暫時確認乘客名單上有一名香港居民，已主動聯絡其家人，並按照當事人家屬意願提供一切可行協助。<br />\n<br />\n《南方都市報》報道，在事故中遇難的中國公民中，包括5男3女，多數是前往肯雅工作的人員，僅有1人是遊客，同時亦包括來自香港的聯合國環境署職員。內地的攜程網則指出，航班上其中一名中國乘客，是來自遼寧本溪。<br />\n<br />\n台灣的外交部則表示，經過查證，涉事航班上沒有台灣人。<br />\n<br />\n外媒拍得一批中國人在機場守候，該批中國人指同事可能在機上。近年，大批中國民眾到非洲工作，埃塞俄比亞航空是他們前往非洲的其中一個主要途徑。一名網民說，中國到埃塞俄比亞的航班，都會在晚上抵達首都亞的斯亞貝巴，然後中國乘客會轉乘其他航班前往非洲各地，「我每次在埃塞俄比亞轉機，幾乎全是中國人」。<br />\n<br />\n埃塞俄比亞航空早前發表聲明，指ET-302航班在當地時間早上8時38分起飛，數分鐘後便失去聯絡，然後於8時44分，在距離亞的斯亞貝巴東南62公里的德布雷塞特（Bishoftu）附近墜毁。航空公司稱，已展開搜索及救援行動，暫時未能確定機上乘客及機組人員的情況，以及客機墜毁原因。"},{"pid":"1665fa65fa992839b4ada25371cad1f45e8c9b56","tid":1055512,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:07:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190310/59353371\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190310%2F59353371&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmNixMN8FcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=7477dcf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190310%2F59353371&h=619a943d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190310/59353371</a>"},{"pid":"06ee96b712e1376d3f7089e9557d1ed7fa6ee918","tid":1055512,"uid":45232,"like":225,"dislike":4,"score":221,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:08:37.000Z","msg":"非洲肯雅聯合國辦事處工作<br />\n<br />\n好似又有個巴打係UN做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580435bea0fe6d6743ea5a6f396c237d557c37e4","tid":1055512,"uid":42751,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知點解諗起蠟筆小新，松阪老師個男朋友"},{"pid":"7fe235ea5ec6dbe7928a5d5e373f6e907bac2fbb","tid":1055512,"uid":29093,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:11:34.000Z","msg":"言談之間又係講樓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港豬"},{"pid":"04455efdf6f1e502d5a0f4b1a0e40d5b38bac3ba","tid":1055512,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:12:54.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"6f220bb52eaef2bb55b1f4d9c7c680ffd8fe05ee","tid":1055512,"uid":73722,"like":63,"dislike":3,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:13:03.000Z","msg":"前兩日先睇完隔離個空難post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n墨菲定律<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3295de646c0e47d4499fe6efb7486db1cfcfc4c","tid":1055512,"uid":28279,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"06ee96b712e1376d3f7089e9557d1ed7fa6ee918","tid":1055512,"uid":45232,"like":225,"dislike":4,"score":221,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:08:37.000Z","msg":"非洲肯雅聯合國辦事處工作<br />\n<br />\n好似又有個巴打係UN做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似真係環境署"},{"pid":"5c9b768ca6e61429123dfb6b09e933b6748b7c16","tid":1055512,"uid":45286,"like":190,"dislike":2,"score":188,"quote":{"pid":"06ee96b712e1376d3f7089e9557d1ed7fa6ee918","tid":1055512,"uid":45232,"like":225,"dislike":4,"score":221,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:08:37.000Z","msg":"非洲肯雅聯合國辦事處工作<br />\n<br />\n好似又有個巴打係UN做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:16:02.000Z","msg":"嗰個巴打報咗平安<br />\n出事嗰個係佢同事"},{"pid":"dbb1d2d907b3ae10c92b33bf1ac6133ebb2d1083","tid":1055512,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225a43e84f33017434be4e74c2bdaf5e40c0a379","tid":1055512,"uid":20933,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:30:51.000Z","msg":"<strong>罹難港人熱愛非洲 妻子於UNESCO工作 一家三口定居肯雅</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190310/large/1552228102_35b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190310%2Flarge%2F1552228102_35b7.jpg&h=8a806517&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n埃塞俄比亞航空一架737-800MAX客機，今日在從首都亞的斯亞貝巴（Addis Ababa），飛往肯雅首都內羅比（Nairobi）途中墜毁，機上149名乘客及8名機組人員，全部罹難。據悉，罹難的8名中國人死者中，包括一名叫「曾成毅」的香港人。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，曾成毅在聯合國環境署工作，現年37歲，他早前前往羅馬探朋友，並在3日前在ig更新個人狀態，豈料今日經埃塞俄比亞轉機返回肯雅時出事。<br />\n<br />\n洋名Victor的曾成毅2000年在觀塘瑪利諾書院中七畢業，之後入讀中文大學工商管理學系，2004年畢業後赴笈倫敦升學，曾於意大利的聯合國糧食及農業組織工作，之後更遠赴非洲肯雅聯合國環境署的辦事處工作。<br />\n<br />\n在去年12月中大校友期刊中，曾成毅曾以校友身份，短暫返回中大擔任全球研究課程其中一節課的客席講師，與學生分享對可持續發展的看法。<br />\n<br />\n另外，曾成毅已婚，與姓張妻子育有一子，一家三口居住在非洲肯雅亞首都內羅比，他經常在fb及ig分享在當地的家庭合照、工作生活及探訪當地大學等照片，而且曾成毅更將自己的fb改名，以「home in nairobi」來表達對該塊非洲土地的鍾愛。<br />\n<br />\n至於，曾成毅的妻子亦在肯雅聯合國教科文組織（UNESCO）教育部門擔任知識管理及信息專家，其姨母曾於網上指曾成毅與妻子在教會結識，兩人一見鐘情，締結良緣，2016年雙雙派駐往肯雅工作，並在當地誕下一子。<br />\n<br />\n入境處根據當地機關提供予大使館的資料，暫時確認乘客名單上有一名香港居民，已主動聯絡其家人，並按當事人家屬意願提供一切可行協助，並透過外交部駐港特派員公署、中國駐埃塞俄比亞民主共和國大使館及有關航空公司了解情況，會繼續與公署、大使館、當事人家屬及航空公司保持聯繫。"},{"pid":"2815969b924a1090f5386ab83a7159f690477d46","tid":1055512,"uid":162160,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:31:39.000Z","msg":"R.i.p<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5aaaefc7de0ed821d5130b9c749e3d94803d378","tid":1055512,"uid":5995,"like":6,"dislike":140,"score":-134,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:34:14.000Z","msg":"留係香港返工就唔會發生呢種事"},{"pid":"9533e10e168ae0778975993febeb415e851289bb","tid":1055512,"uid":74172,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:34:20.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ea341e34f4294181a6d6f58d315c5e4abd5528","tid":1055512,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:34:45.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb0eafeebcc6f17f5add3427ed1932a831e67a0","tid":1055512,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:36:50.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"4a83db1d7d8bb6aeffa72f451f37e82c6b4fe9be","tid":1055512,"uid":197640,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:37:46.000Z","msg":"RIP <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" c